date_groupby = train.groupby(by='date').sum()[ride_columns].reset_index()
date_groupby['day'] = date_groupby['date'].dt.day
temp = np.array(ride_columns[:-1]).reshape(4,3)

fig, ax = plt.subplots(4, 3, figsize=(15, 15))
plt.subplots_adjust(hspace=0.5, wspace=0.2)
for i in range(4):
    for j in range(3):
        g = sns.lineplot(data = date_groupby, x='day', y=date_groupby[temp[i, j]], ax=ax[i, j])
        g.set_title(temp[i,j])
        g.set_ylabel('')
        g.set_ylim((0, 17500))
        # g.set_xticklabels(g.get_xticklabels(), rotation=45)

plt.show()

        g.set_ylabel('')

def point(data):
    for i in range(len(data)):
        data['latlong'][i] = Point(data['longitude'][i], data['latitude'][i])
    return data

def Sep_hol(x):
    if x == 12 or x==13 or x==14:
        return 1
    else:
        return 0
        
def Oct_hol(x):
    if x == 3 or x==9 :
        return 1
    else:
        return 0

bagging_predict_result = [] #   
for _ in range(10):
    data_index = [data_index for data_index in range(X.shape[0])] #     
    random_data_index = np.random.choice(data_index, X.shape[0]) #  1/10   , //    
    print(len(set(random_data_index)))
    lgb_dtrain = lgb.Dataset(data = X.iloc[random_data_index,], label = y.iloc[random_data_index,]) #   LightGBM   
    lgb_param = {'max_depth': 14, #  
            'learning_rate': 0.01, # Step Size
            'n_estimators': 500, # Number of trees,   
            'objective': 'regression'} #  , Label must be in [0, num_class) -> num_class 1 .
